# Database Example

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values.

```env
# Database (Neon PostgreSQL)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:5432/impactos?sslmode=require

# Email Service (Resend)
RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxx
FROM_EMAIL=noreply@yourdomain.com

# AI Scoring (Anthropic Claude)
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-xxxxxxxxxx

# Payments (Paystack)
PAYSTACK_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_xxxxxxxxxx
PAYSTACK_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_xxxxxxxxxx

# Authentication
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-here

# CORS Origins (comma-separated)
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:3001

# Optional: Storage (Cloudflare R2)
R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID=
R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=
R2_BUCKET_NAME=impact-os-evidence
R2_ENDPOINT=https://xxxxx.r2.cloudflarestorage.com
```
